phallus, lateral 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="425">E</emphasis>
phallus dorsal. Modified from 
<bibRefCitation author="Harris, SC" journalOrPublisher="Insecta Mundi" pageId="0" pageNumber="425" pagination="1 - 54" refId="B13" refString="Harris, SC, Armitage, BJ, 2019. The Trichoptera of Panama. X. The Quebrada Rambala Drainage, with description of 19 new species of microcaddisfies (Trichoptera: Hydroptilidae). Insecta Mundi 0707: 1 - 54" title="The Trichoptera of Panama. X. The Quebrada Rambala Drainage, with description of 19 new species of microcaddisfies (Trichoptera: Hydroptilidae)." volume="0707" year="2019">Harris and Armitage (2019)</bibRefCitation>
